video.title: Unsealed: Alien Files
video.synopsis: Each episode of this chilling series reveals newly declassified truths about extraterrestrial visitation, close encounters and government cover-ups.

episodes.synopsis: Insiders discuss the existence of a book detailing the collaboration of the military with alien forces and the mechanics of its cover-up.
episodes.title: Alien Encyclopedia

episodes.synopsis: In addition to physical visitation, aliens have sent messages to Earth for thousands of years. Now, one of those transmissions has been deciphered.
episodes.title: Cracking The Alien Code

episodes.synopsis: Revisit alien encounters in Los Angeles and learn why the city has been a magnet for alien visitations.
episodes.title: UFO Portal Los Angeles

episodes.synopsis: The Vatican has one of the oldest and largest libraries of arcana on Earth. Could it hold secrets of alien visitation?
episodes.title: Aliens & the Vatican

episodes.synopsis: This episode examines evidence in NASA archives that the race to the moon was based on knowledge of an alien presence there.
episodes.title: Aliens On the Moon

episodes.synopsis: This episode examines the often unexplained illnesses that have plagued mankind throughout history and the possibility that they are of alien origin.
episodes.title: Alien Plagues

episodes.synopsis: Experts examine modern technology for evidence of alien involvement and ponder what mankind exchanged for such marvels.
episodes.title: Secret Alien Technology

episodes.synopsis: This episode spotlights 10 of the most famous alien encounters and re-examines them in light of newly released information.
episodes.title: Top 10 Alien Encounters

episodes.synopsis: Experts reveal physical and medical evidence of alien mind-control implants and what it means for our concept of free will.
episodes.title: Alien Implants

episodes.synopsis: Explore evidence that the Nazis' quest for world domination was aided by alien technology, and find out where that technology is today.
episodes.title: Nazis and UFOs

episodes.synopsis: Some believe that the government may be filled with not only human beings complicit with an alien cover-up, but actual aliens in human disguise.
episodes.title: Aliens Among Us

episodes.synopsis: This episode delves into the evidence of an alien visitation from the 1960s, including a stunning photograph and a failed nuclear launch.
episodes.title: The Solway Firth Spaceman

episodes.synopsis: Insiders discuss what U.S. presidents have known about alien visitation and technology, and what that means for national security.
episodes.title: Aliens and Presidents

episodes.synopsis: This episode examines the colossal structures that emerged from ancient Egypt and the involvement of alien technology in their construction.
episodes.title: Alien Gods Of Egypt

episodes.synopsis: This episode counts down the 10 most popular theories on alien encounters, including the reasons for and effects of extraterrestrial visitation.
episodes.title: Top 10 Alien Plots

episodes.synopsis: This episode examines the possibility that human life began on Mars and was relocated to Earth in the ancient past.
episodes.title: Life on Mars

episodes.synopsis: Are the imposing figures who appear at alien visitation sites agents of the government -- or do they represent something more sinister?
episodes.title: Men in Black

episodes.synopsis: This episode explores one of the key elements of alien visitation phenomena: the role of the military in investigation, complicity and cover-up.
episodes.title: Aliens and the Military

episodes.synopsis: Visit Roswell, New Mexico, the world's most famous alien crash site and home to Area 51, where many believe the government keeps alien technology.
episodes.title: Roswell and Area 51

episodes.synopsis: Nearly every country on the planet has its forbidden places. Could these restricted areas be where alien technology and other evidence is stored?
episodes.title: Forbidden Places

episodes.synopsis: Insiders from the United Kingdom discuss the cover-up of alien visitation evidence by the government and the military.
episodes.title: British X-Files

episodes.synopsis: This episode reveals "hot spots" for alien activity around the globe and what makes those sites magnets for visitation.
episodes.title: Alien Hot Spots
